message.text:
“𝐃𝐞𝐚𝐫 𝐒𝐚𝐧𝐭𝐚, 𝐈’𝐦 𝐠𝐞𝐭𝐭𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐫𝐞𝐚𝐝𝐲 𝐭𝐨 𝐰𝐫𝐢𝐭𝐞 𝐦𝐲 𝐥𝐞𝐭𝐭𝐞𝐫…”

Have you started yours yet? With only 𝟏𝟎𝟎 𝐝𝐚𝐲𝐬 𝐥𝐞𝐟𝐭 𝐮𝐧𝐭𝐢𝐥 𝐂𝐡𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐭𝐦𝐚𝐬, now is the perfect time to gather your thoughts and share your stories—whether they’re little mistakes, big hopes, or kind gestures that deserve a spot on Santa’s list. 

This countdown isn’t just about the days left; it’s about capturing the magic, reflecting on the year, and preparing for a season filled with joy and wonder. 

So, what will your letter say this year? Let the holiday spirit begin!🎄

Caption by: Patrick Blas
Pubmat by: Layza Tolomia

message.text:
“𝐃𝐞𝐚𝐫 𝐒𝐚𝐧𝐭𝐚, 𝐈’𝐦 𝐠𝐞𝐭𝐭𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐫𝐞𝐚𝐝𝐲 𝐭𝐨 𝐰𝐫𝐢𝐭𝐞 𝐦𝐲 𝐥𝐞𝐭𝐭𝐞𝐫…”

Have you started yours yet? With only 𝟏𝟎𝟎 𝐝𝐚𝐲𝐬 𝐥𝐞𝐟𝐭 𝐮𝐧𝐭𝐢𝐥 𝐂𝐡𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐭𝐦𝐚𝐬, now is the perfect time to gather your thoughts and share your stories—whether they’re little mistakes, big hopes, or kind gestures that deserve a spot on Santa’s list. 

This countdown isn’t just about the days left; it’s about capturing the magic, reflecting on the year, and preparing for a season filled with joy and wonder. 

So, what will your letter say this year? Let the holiday spirit begin!🎄

Caption by: Patrick Blas
Pubmat by: Layza Tolomia
